  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="AN200.1-kilavi">talaimakaḷ kuṟippaṟinta tōḻi talaimakaṟkuk kuṟainayappak kūṟiyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">How the confidante who had understood HER intention said to HIM that [his] request would be granted.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AN200.1">
        <l>nilāvi ṉilaṅku maṇaṉmali maṟukiṟ</l>
        <l>pulālañ cērip pulvēy kurampai</l>
        <l>yūreṉa vuṇarāc ciṟumaiyoṭu nīruṭut</l>
        <l>tiṉṉā vuṟaiyuṭ ṭāyiṉu miṉpa</l>
        <l>morunā ḷuṟaintici ṉōrkkum vaḻināṭ</l>
        <l>ṭampati maṟakkum paṇpi ṉempati</l>
        <l>vantaṉai ceymō vaḷaimēy parappa</l>
        <l>pommaṟ paṭuti<supplied>rai</supplied> kammeṉa vuṭaitaru</l>
        <l>maraṉōṅ koruciṟaip palapā rāṭṭi</l>
        <l>yellai yemmoṭu kaḻippi yellu</l>
        <l>naṟṟēr pūṭṭalu muriyī raṟṟaṉṟu</l>
        <l>cērntaṉir celkuvī rāyiṉ yāmu</l>
        <l>memvarai yaḷavaiyiṟ peṭkuvōmatu</l>
        <l>nummop patuvō <supplied>vurait</supplied>tici ṉemakkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Even if it [is] not a pleasing abode, (4a-c)</l>
        <l>encircled by water, of a smallness as not to be perceived as a village, (3)</l>
        <l>with [its] grass-covered huts in a quarter reeking of fish, (2)</l>
        <l>in a street full of sand, shining like moonlight, – (1)</l>
        <l>please act, you who have come (7ab)</l>
        <l>to our place, of a kind [that is] a pleasure to whoever has</l>
        <l>stayed a single day, that makes [them] forget their own place the next day! (4d-6)</l>
        <l>After spending the day time with us, (10a-c)</l>
        <l>having appreciated many things in a spot high-grown with trees, (9)</l>
        <l>where the waves of the expanse grazed by shells,</l>
        <l>coming in thick [and] breaking quietly, (7cdf.)</l>
        <l>at night too you have to yoke [your] good chariot. If it is not so (10f.)</l>
        <l>[and] you were to go [and] join [us], we all of us(?) (12)</l>
        <l>would protect [you], according to our limits. (13)</l>
        <l>Is [this] agreeable to you? Tell us! (14)</l>
      </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
